OL,3,CFather failed to check teenage
OL,4,Cdaughter's bag on day of school
OL,5,Cstabbing
OL,7,FThe father of a teenager, accused of
OL,8,Fthe attempted murder of two teachers
OL,9,Fand a pupil during a school stabbing
OL,10,Fin Ammanford, failed to check her bag
OL,11,Fon the day of the attack.
OL,13,FThe defendant's father told a jury at
OL,14,FSwansea Crown Court how he had agreed
OL,15,Fto check her school bag each morning,
OL,16,Fas well as remove dangerous knives
OL,17,Ffrom his house, after his daughter was
OL,18,Fsuspended from Ysgol Dyffryn Aman for
OL,19,Fcarrying a knife in school in
OL,20,FSeptember 2023.
