OL,5,Cstabbing
OL,7,FThe pupil's father told the court: "I
OL,8,Fdidn't manage to search her bag before
OL,9,Fshe left, I hadn't got up after
OL,10,Ffinishing work late."
OL,12,FAsked if he noticed any knives missing
OL,13,Ffrom his home on the day of the attack
OL,14,Fthe pupil's father replied, "no".
OL,16,FIn court, the jury was shown the knife
OL,17,Fused in the attack that injured two
OL,18,Fteachers and a pupil, requiring them
OL,19,Fto need hospital treatment.
