OL,7,FUnder cross-examination, the father
OL,8,Fsaid how his daughter had been
OL,9,Fsubjected to bullying, which had
OL,10,Fcaused her to move to Ysgol Dyffryn
OL,11,FAman from another school.
OL,13,FHe told the court pupils had followed
OL,14,Fher home, hit her in the back of the
OL,15,Fhead as well as thrown eggs at the
OL,16,Ffamily home and attempted to break in.
