OL,7,FAsked how the defendant reacted when
OL,8,Fshe returned home from school her
OL,9,Ffather said: "She would come home
OL,10,Fevery evening upset because people had
OL,11,Fbeen hitting her on the bus, calling
OL,12,Fher a weirdo.
OL,14,F"Sometimes she would come back and she
OL,15,Fwould be frightened by the amount of
OL,16,Fpeople who didn't like her."
OL,18,FThe trial continues.
